{"tid":2448262,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"政府向美國領事館發強檢公告","createTime":"2021-03-15T20:21:24.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-16T07:58:54.000Z","uid":132859,"like":22,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"12c31d320b766f5fdb6c8527954c41dc3c41bf7d","tid":2448262,"uid":132859,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T20:21:24.000Z","msg":"URSUS Fitness群組持續擴大，令多名居港外籍人士染疫。美國駐港總領事館（總領事館）今午（15日）公佈，兩名職員確診武漢肺炎，而兩人的工作性質不會接觸公眾。總領事館續稱，即日起停止總領事館服務作深層清潔，未來兩天（16及17日）的簽證申請將會取消。衞生防護中心表明，會與其他有確診個案的工作場所一樣，將領事館納入強制檢測。<br />\n...<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210315/PBRP2YS2EJB3NLWKI6HWGVIXKE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210315%2FPBRP2YS2EJB3NLWKI6HWGVIXKE%2F&d=HziU8jWK8j2Oa3ZLfTDirA5Iyec62GFiithg4eFnous%3D&h=7f9009ca\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210315%2FPBRP2YS2EJB3NLWKI6HWGVIXKE%2F&h=4786f630\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210315/PBRP2YS2EJB3NLWKI6HWGVIXKE/</a><br />\n<br />\n以為喺美國領土就冇事？<br />\n快啲叫班CIA外站人員出嚟俾我哋收集DNA樣本同埋對名<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ee38f1d5aa350f487e178f1974382ddc7605a06","tid":2448262,"uid":199689,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T20:22:37.000Z","msg":"留名睇下美國點回應<br />\n香港法律cover成個宇宙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8abc85e0098fbc6ee6d1afce676f47b90610952","tid":2448262,"uid":231522,"like":4,"dislike":3,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T20:22:57.000Z","msg":"左膠： 會配合"},{"pid":"49a5985b50ce1255b018cd1d0de99ee99e3bffd6","tid":2448262,"uid":82052,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T20:29:26.000Z","msg":"領事館會合作，可以用美國政府認可檢測機構做。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6366bcebe9edf40e6bc1ff686ed